            <title><![CDATA[Assassin's Creed Shadows Director Reveals Why Game Was Delayed A Second Time]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/assassins-creed-shadows-director-reveals-why-game-was-delayed-a-second-time/1100-6528995/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
